z-report .kz-hero-text p { margin: 6px 0; }\n@media (max-width: 640px) {\n  .kz-report .kz-domain-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }\n  .kz-report .kz-type-badge { font-size: 18px; padding: 8px 14px; }\n  .kz-report .kz-hero-illustration { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }\n  .kz-report .kz-hero-illustration svg { width: 140px; height: 105px; }\n}\n.kz-report { counter-reset: kz-section; }\n.kz-report h2.kz-section { counter-increment: kz-section; counter-reset: kz-subsection; }\n.kz-report h2.kz-section::before { content: counter(kz-section, simp-chinese-informal) \"、\"; font-weight: 700; color: inherit; }\n.kz-report h3.kz-subsection { counter-increment: kz-subsection; }\n.kz-report h3.kz-subsection::before { content: counter(kz-section) \".\" counter(kz-subsection) \" \"; font-weight: 700; color: inherit; }\n.kz-report .kz-screen-only { }\n@media print {\n  .kz-report .kz-print-btn { display: none; }\n  .kz-report { max-width: 100%; }\n  .kz-report h2 { page-break-after: avoid; }\n  .kz-report table { page-break-inside: avoid; }\n  .kz-report .kz-card, .kz-report .kz-highlight, .kz-report .kz-tip, .kz-report .kz-warning, .kz-report .kz-type-card, .kz-report .kz-chart-card, .kz-report .kz-domain-block, .kz-report .kz-illustration-card, .kz-report .kz-hero-illustration { page-break-inside: avoid; }\n  .kz-report .kz-screen-only { display: none !important; }\n  .kz-report .kz-screen-only h2.kz-section { counter-increment: none; }\n}\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"kz-print-header\">\n  <h1>学生一页纸测评摘要 | Student One-Page Summary</h1>\n  <button class=\"kz-print-btn\" onclick=\"window.print()\">🖨️ 打印 / Print</button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"kz-meta\">\n  <p><strong>姓名 / Name</strong>：低方差作答者</p>\n  <p><strong>Holland 三码 / Holland Code</strong>：<strong>CRI</strong> — 常规型（Conventional）</p>\n  <p><strong>优势领域 / Leading Strength Domain</strong>：影响力</p>\n  <p><strong>优势风格 / Strengths Style</strong>：推动影响型 / Influential Mobilizer</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"kz-warning kz-screen-only\">\n  <strong>数据质量提示 / Data Quality Notes</strong>\n  <ul class=\"kz-list\">\n    <li>你的 Holland 得分区分度较低（各类型分数接近），三码可能不能清晰代表你的兴趣偏好，建议结合日常经历进一步验证。/ Your Holland scores show low differentiation (types are close together), so the three-letter code may not clearly represent your interests. Validate against your daily experiences.</li><li>检测到大量相同答案，疑似直线作答或敷衍，建议重新认真测评。 / Many identical answers detected (possible straight-lining or rushing). Please retake carefully.</li><li>答案明显偏向 A 侧或 B 侧，可能存在理解偏差或敷衍。 / Responses are strongly biased toward one side; possible misunderstanding or rushing.</li><li>Gallup 模拟量表 A/B 双侧映射已完整（双侧计分题 98.3%，34/34 个主题参与计分）。结果为探索性参考，非官方 CliftonStrengths 报告。/ Gallup simulation has full A/B mapping (dual-side 98.3%, 34/34 themes scored). Results are for exploration—not an official CliftonStrengths report.</li>\n  </ul>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"kz-synthesis\">\n  <h3>综合解读与给你的建议 | Summary & Recommendations</h3>\n  <p><strong>低方差作答者</strong>，你好。以下是对你本次双维度测评的综合解读——帮你把「喜欢做什么」和「擅长怎么做」放在一起看。</p>\n  <p class=\"kz-en\"><em>Hello <strong>低方差作答者</strong>. This section integrates what you enjoy doing with how you naturally work best.</em></p>\n\n  <h4>你是谁：兴趣舞台 + 优势风格 | Who You Are</h4>\n  <p>你的 Holland 三码是 <strong>CRI</strong>，兴趣舞台标签为 <strong>秩序组织派 / Order Organizer</strong>；Gallup 主导优势领域是 <strong>影响力</strong>（次要领域：战略思维），工作风格偏向 <strong>推动影响型 / Influential Mobilizer</strong>。</p>\n  <p>Top 5 才干主题：竞争、排难、回顾、分析、伯乐</p>\n  <ul class=\"kz-list\">\n    <li><strong>C</strong>（常规型（Conventional））— 最感兴趣：喜欢处理数据、文件、细节和规范化流程，重视准确性、条理性和稳定性。</li>\n<li><strong>R</strong>（现实型（Realistic））— 次感兴趣：喜欢使用工具、机器或体力技能解决实际问题，重视具体成果。</li>\n<li><strong>I</strong>（研究型（Investigative））— 第三感兴趣：喜欢观察、学习、研究、分析、评估和解决问题，重视独立思考和知识探索。</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h4>兴趣与优势如何配合 | How Interests & Strengths Fit</h4>\n  <p>你的优势领域（影响力）与 Holland 兴趣舞台（CRI）存在一定张力，建议通过具体项目体验来验证真实偏好，避免过早定性。 / Your strength domain (影响力) and interest stage (CRI) show some tension. Validate your real preferences through concrete projects before committing too early.</p>\n  <p><strong>整体契合度 / Overall Fit</strong>：兴趣与优势存在张力，需项目验证 / Tension to explore through projects</p>\n  <p class=\"kz-small\">三码在六边形上相对集中，兴趣轮廓较为清晰。/ Your three-letter code is relatively consistent on the hexagon.</p>\n\n  <div class=\"kz-synthesis-advice\">\n    <p><strong>给你的三条建议 / Three Recommendations for You</strong></p>\n    <ol class=\"kz-list\">\n      <li>尝试整理一份复杂资料或完成一项需要细致核对的事务，观察你对流程与准确性的感受。/ Try organizing complex information or completing detail-heavy work and observe how you feel about process and accuracy.</li><li>练习用 3 分钟清晰表达一个观点，并观察听众的反应——你的优势在「推动他人行动」。/ Practice expressing one idea clearly in 3 minutes and observe how others respond—your strength is mobilizing action.</li><li>你的兴趣与优势存在差异或张力，不必强行统一——寻找能把两者结合起来的具体场景（如跨学科项目、复合岗位）。/ Your interests and strengths show tension—don't force them to match; look for roles or projects that combine both.</li>\n    </ol>\n  </div>\n\n  <p>结合以上解读，当前最值得你留意的探索方向包括：<strong>技术产品经理、行业分析师、销售运营经理</strong>。请从下方「稳妥入口职业」和「核心推荐专业」中挑选 1–2 个，用真实体验去验证——喜欢不等于适合，适合也需要在实践中确认。</p>\n  <p class=\"kz-en\"><em>Based on this profile, directions worth exploring include: <strong>技术产品经理、行业分析师、销售运营经理</strong>. Pick 1–2 from the safe-entry careers and core majors below, and validate through real experience.</em></p>\n\n  <div class=\"kz-ethics\">\n    <p><strong>重要提醒 / Important Reminder</strong>：本报告是<strong>探索与自我发现的辅助工具</strong>，不能替代你的判断，也不能限制你的可能性。测评结果会随经历与成长而变化——请带着好奇而非焦虑阅读，并与信任的老师、家长或咨询师讨论你的下一步。</p>\n    <p class=\"kz-en\"><em>This report is an <strong>exploration aid</strong>, not a verdict on who you must become. Results can evolve with experience—read with curiosity, not anxiety, and discuss your next steps with trusted adults or counselors.</em></p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n    <div class=\"kz-type-card\" style=\"border-left: 6px solid #6b7280;\">\n      <div class=\"kz-type-badges\">\n        <span class=\"kz-type-badge kz-holland-badge\" style=\"background:#6b7280;\">CRI</span>\n        <span class=\"kz-type-plus\">+</span>\n        <span class=\"kz-type-badge kz-domain-badge\" style=\"background:#f59e0b;\">影响力</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"kz-type-summary\">\n        <strong>秩序组织派 / Order Organizer</strong> × <strong>推动影响型</strong>\n        <br><span class=\"kz-en\">Order Organizer × Influential Mobilizer</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    \n\n\n    <div class=\"kz-hero-illustration\">\n      <div class=\"kz-illustration-row\" style=\"margin:0;\">\n        <div class=\"kz-illustration-card\" style=\"max-width:180px;\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 160 120\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n      <rect width=\"160\" height=\"120\" rx=\"12\" fill=\"#f3f4f6\"/>\n      <circle cx=\"80\" cy=\"60\" r=\"28\" fill=\"#6b7280\" opacity=\"0.15\"/>\n      <rect x=\"52\" y=\"42\" width=\"36\" height=\"48\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#6b7280\" stroke-width=\"4\"/>\n      <rect x=\"60\" y=\"52\" width=\"20\" height=\"4\" rx=\"1\" fill=\"#6b7280\"/>\n      <rect x=\"60\" y=\"60\" width=\"20\" height=\"4\" rx=\"1\" fill=\"#6b7280\"/>\n      <rect x=\"60\" y=\"68\" width=\"14\" height=\"4\" rx=\"1\" fill=\"#6b7280\"/>\n      <path d=\"M95 50 L125 50\" stroke=\"#6b7280\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n      <path d=\"M95 60 L118 60\" stroke=\"#6b7280\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n      <path d=\"M95 70 L115 70\" stroke=\"#6b7280\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n    </svg>\n          <div class=\"kz-illustration-label\">秩序组织派</div>\n          <div class=\"kz-illustration-en\">Order Organizer</div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"kz-illustration-card\" style=\"max-width:180px;\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 160 120\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n      <rect width=\"160\" height=\"120\" rx=\"12\" fill=\"#fef3c7\"/>\n      <circle cx=\"80\" cy=\"60\" r=\"28\" fill=\"#f59e0b\" opacity=\"0.15\"/>\n      <path d=\"M52 55 L52 75 L68 70 L68 50 Z\" fill=\"#f59e0b\"/>\n      <path d=\"M68 55 L95 48\" stroke=\"#f59e0b\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n      <path d=\"M95 35 L95 65\" stroke=\"#f59e0b\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n      <ellipse cx=\"95\" cy=\"50\" rx=\"10\" ry=\"18\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#f59e0b\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n      <circle cx=\"115\" cy=\"50\" r=\"12\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#f59e0b\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n    </svg>\n          <div class=\"kz-illustration-label\">影响力</div>\n          <div class=\"kz-illustration-en\">Influencing</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"kz-hero-text\">\n        <p><strong>你的组合画像 / Your Profile</strong></p>\n        <p>兴趣舞台：秩序组织派（Order Organizer）；优势领域：影响力 / Influencing。</p>\n        <p class=\"kz-en\">Interest stage: Order Organizer; Leading strength domain: Influencing.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    \n\n<h2>1. 我的测评画像 | My Profile</h2>\n\n<div class=\"kz-chart-card\">\n  <div class=\"kz-chart-title\">Holland 兴趣六维得分 | RIASEC Scores</div>\n  <div class=\"kz-chart-subtitle\">分数越高，代表该类型越能描述你的兴趣倾向 / Higher scores mean stronger alignment with that interest type.</div>\n  <svg width=\"100%\" height=\"224\" viewBox=\"0 0 420 224\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><rect x=\"70\" y=\"10\" width=\"300\" height=\"22\" rx=\"11\" fill=\"#fee2e2\"/><rect x=\"70\" y=\"10\" width=\"290.3225806451613\" height=\"22\" rx=\"11\" fill=\"#ef4444\"/><text x=\"60\" y=\"26.0\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"600\" fill=\"#374151\">现实型 R</text><text x=\"368.3225806451613\" y=\"26.0\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"600\" fill=\"#374151\">30</text><rect x=\"70\" y=\"44\" width=\"300\" height=\"22\" rx=\"11\" fill=\"#dbeafe\"/><rect x=\"70\" y=\"44\" width=\"290.3225806451613\" height=\"22\" rx=\"11\" fill=\"#3b82f6\"/><text x=\"60\" y=\"60.0\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"600\" fill=\"#374151\">研究型 I</text><text x=\"368.3225806451613\" y=\"60.0\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"600\" fill=\"#374151\">30</text><rect x=\"70\" y=\"78\" width=\"300\" height=\"22\" rx=\"11\" fill=\"#ede9fe\"/><rect x=\"70\" y=\"78\" width=\"290.3225806451613\" height=\"22\" rx=\"11\" fill=\"#8b5cf6\"/><text x=\"60\" y=\"94.0\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"600\" fill=\"#374151\">艺术型 A</text><text x=\"368.3225806451613\" y=\"94.0\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"600\" fill=\"#374151\">30</text><rect x=\"70\" y=\"112\" width=\"300\" height=\"22\" rx=\"11\" fill=\"#dcfce7\"/><rect x=\"70\" y=\"112\" width=\"270.96774193548384\" height=\"22\" rx=\"11\" fill=\"#22c55e\"/><text x=\"60\" y=\"128.0\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"600\" fill=\"#374151\">社会型 S</text><text x=\"348.96774193548384\" y=\"128.0\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"600\" fill=\"#374151\">28</text><rect x=\"70\" y=\"146\" width=\"300\" height=\"22\" rx=\"11\" fill=\"#fef3c7\"/><rect x=\"70\" y=\"146\" width=\"251.61290322580646\" height=\"22\" rx=\"11\" fill=\"#f59e0b\"/><text x=\"60\" y=\"162.0\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"600\" fill=\"#374151\">企业型 E</text><text x=\"329.61290322580646\" y=\"162.0\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"600\" fill=\"#374151\">26</text><rect x=\"70\" y=\"180\" width=\"300\" height=\"22\" rx=\"11\" fill=\"#f3f4f6\"/><rect x=\"70\" y=\"180\" width=\"300.0\" height=\"22\" rx=\"11\" fill=\"#6b7280\"/><text x=\"60\" y=\"196.0\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"600\" fill=\"#374151\">常规型 C</text><text x=\"378.0\" y=\"196.0\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"600\" fill=\"#374151\">31</text></svg>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"kz-chart-card\">\n  <div class=\"kz-chart-title\">Gallup 优势领域 | CliftonStrengths Domains</div>\n  <div class=\"kz-chart-subtitle\">主导领域是你最自然的工作方式，次要领域是其次 / Your leading domain is your most natural way of working.</div>\n  <div class=\"kz-domain-grid\">\n        <div class=\"kz-domain-block\" style=\"background:#fee2e2; border-top: 4px solid #ef4444;\">\n          <div class=\"kz-domain-name\">执行力</div>\n          <div class=\"kz-domain-en\">Executing</div>\n          \n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"kz-domain-block\" style=\"background:#fef3c7; border-top: 4px solid #f59e0b;\">\n          <div class=\"kz-domain-name\">影响力</div>\n          <div class=\"kz-domain-en\">Influencing</div>\n          <span class=\"kz-domain-badge kz-domain-primary\">主导</span>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"kz-domain-block\" style=\"background:#dcfce7; border-top: 4px solid #22c55e;\">\n          <div class=\"kz-domain-name\">关系建立</div>\n          <div class=\"kz-domain-en\">Relationship Building</div>\n          \n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"kz-domain-block\" style=\"background:#dbeafe; border-top: 4px solid #3b82f6;\">\n          <div class=\"kz-domain-name\">战略思维</div>\n          <div class=\"kz-domain-en\">Strategic Thinking</div>\n          <span class=\"kz-domain-badge kz-domain-secondary\">次要</span>\n        </div>\n        </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"kz-chart-card\">\n  <div class=\"kz-chart-title\">Top 5 才干主题 | My Top 5 Themes</div>\n  <div class=\"kz-chart-subtitle\">颜色代表该主题所属的优势领域 / Colors show which domain each theme belongs to.</div>\n  <div class=\"kz-top5-pills\">\n        <div class=\"kz-top5-pill\" style=\"background:#f59e0b20; border: 1px solid #f59e0b; color:#f59e0b;\">\n          <span class=\"kz-top5-rank\">1</span>\n          <span class=\"kz-top5-name\">竞争</span>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"kz-top5-pill\" style=\"background:#ef444420; border: 1px solid #ef4444; color:#ef4444;\">\n          <span class=\"kz-top5-rank\">2</span>\n          <span class=\"kz-top5-name\">排难</span>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"kz-top5-pill\" style=\"background:#3b82f620; border: 1px solid #3b82f6; color:#3b82f6;\">\n          <span class=\"kz-top5-rank\">3</span>\n          <span class=\"kz-top5-name\">回顾</span>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"kz-top5-pill\" style=\"background:#3b82f620; border: 1px solid #3b82f6; color:#3b82f6;\">\n          <span class=\"kz-top5-rank\">4</span>\n          <span class=\"kz-top5-name\">分析</span>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"kz-top5-pill\" style=\"background:#22c55e20; border: 1px solid #22c55e; color:#22c55e;\">\n          <span class=\"kz-top5-rank\">5</span>\n          <span class=\"kz-top5-name\">伯乐</span>\n        </div>\n        </div>\n</div>\n\n<h2>2. 我的核心结果 | My Core Results</h2>\n<table>\n  <tr><th>维度 / Dimension</th><th>结果 / Result</th></tr>\n  <tr><td>Holland 三码 / Holland Code</td><td><strong>CRI</strong> — 常规型（Conventional）</td></tr>\n  <tr><td>优势领域 / Leading Strength Domain</td><td>影响力</td></tr>\n  <tr><td>优势风格 / Strengths Style</td><td>推动影响型 / Influential Mobilizer</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n\n        <div class=\"kz-illustration-card\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 160 120\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n      <rect width=\"160\" height=\"120\" rx=\"12\" fill=\"#f3f4f6\"/>\n      <circle cx=\"80\" cy=\"60\" r=\"28\" fill=\"#6b7280\" opacity=\"0.15\"/>\n      <rect x=\"52\" y=\"42\" width=\"36\" height=\"48\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#6b7280\" stroke-width=\"4\"/>\n      <rect x=\"60\" y=\"52\" width=\"20\" height=\"4\" rx=\"1\" fill=\"#6b7280\"/>\n      <rect x=\"60\" y=\"60\" width=\"20\" height=\"4\" rx=\"1\" fill=\"#6b7280\"/>\n      <rect x=\"60\" y=\"68\" width=\"14\" height=\"4\" rx=\"1\" fill=\"#6b7280\"/>\n      <path d=\"M95 50 L125 50\" stroke=\"#6b7280\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n      <path d=\"M95 60 L118 60\" stroke=\"#6b7280\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n      <path d=\"M95 70 L115 70\" stroke=\"#6b7280\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n    </svg>\n          <div class=\"kz-illustration-label\">秩序组织派</div>\n          <div class=\"kz-illustration-en\">Order Organizer</div>\n        </div>\n        \n\n<h2>3. 稳妥入口职业 | Safe Entry Points</h2>\n<p>如果你更关注就业稳定性和现实可行性，以下方向是不错的起点。</p>\n<p class=\"kz-en\">If you prioritize employment stability and practical entry paths, these roles are good starting points.</p>\n<table>\n  <tr><th>职业 / Career</th><th>标签 / Tag</th><th>相关专业 / Related Majors</th></tr>\n  \n        <tr>\n          <td>行业分析师</td>\n          <td><span class=\"kz-tag kz-tag-explore\">探索型 / Explore-oriented</span></td>\n          <td>经济学、金融学、商业分析、统计学、产业经济学</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>技术产品经理</td>\n          <td><span class=\"kz-tag kz-tag-explore\">探索型 / Explore-oriented</span></td>\n          <td>产品设计、计算机科学、工商管理、心理学、工业设计</td>\n        </tr>\n</table>\n\n<h2>4. 核心推荐专业 | Core Recommended Majors</h2>\n<table>\n  <tr><th>专业 / Major</th><th>国内可报说明 / Domestic Note</th><th>海外方向（以英国为例）/ Overseas Example (UK)</th></tr>\n  \n        <tr>\n          <td>产品设计</td>\n          <td>艺术学</td>\n          <td>建议按具体院校查询 / Check programme titles</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>计算机科学</td>\n          <td>理学/工学 / 工学（计算机类）</td>\n          <td>建议按具体院校查询 / Check programme titles</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>工商管理</td>\n          <td>按具体院校招生目录查询</td>\n          <td>建议按具体院校查询 / Check programme titles</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>心理学</td>\n          <td>教育学/理学</td>\n          <td>建议按具体院校查询 / Check programme titles</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>工业设计</td>\n          <td>艺术学</td>\n          <td>建议按具体院校查询 / Check programme titles</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>经济学</td>\n          <td>经济学/管理学</td>\n          <td>建议按具体院校查询 / Check programme titles</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>金融学</td>\n          <td>经济学/管理学</td>\n          <td>建议按具体院校查询 / Check programme titles</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>商业分析</td>\n          <td>按具体院校招生目录查询</td>\n          <td>建议按具体院校查询 / Check programme titles</td>\n        </tr>\n</table>\n\n<h2>5. 三个下一步行动 | Three Next Steps</h2>\n<ul class=\"kz-list\">\n  <li>整理一个复杂数据集或档案：体验分类、核对与流程化的工作。/ Organize a complex dataset or archive to experience categorization, verification, and process work.</li><li>了解一个数据处理或行政管理类专业：如会计、审计、信息系统等。/ Explore a data-processing or administrative major such as accounting, auditing, or information systems.</li><li>准备一次 3 分钟的观点分享，练习清晰表达与说服。/ Prepare a 3-minute point of view sharing to practice clear expression and persuasion.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"kz-tip\">\n  📄 <strong>完整报告 / Full Report</strong>：请查看专业版报告获取 RIASEC 剖面、主题叙事、交叉矩阵与详细专业映射。\n  <br><span class=\"kz-en\">See the professional report for RIASEC profile, theme narrative, cross-matrix, and detailed major mappings.</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n",
